title: Kids' Fun and Healthy Cookbook by Nicola Graimes
description:
Put the fun back into healthy eating with this bright and colorful cookbook. This lively collection encourages kids to consider what they eat and how it affects their bodies, without preaching. 

Yummy interpretations of old classics, as well as new recipes destined to become classic help turn eating into a delicious treat.

Genre: Non-Fiction, Cookery
